query:
INSERT INTO plan_conversations (
                    id,
                    task_id,
                    question_id,
                    question_text,
                    answer,
                    answered_by
                ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                RETURNING
                    id as "id!: Uuid",
                    task_id as "task_id!: Uuid",
                    question_id,
                    question_text,
                    answer,
                    answered_by,
                    answered_at as "answered_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
